CLCascade
=========

CLCascade is a library to create twitter-like UI in iPad apps created by CreativeLabs.pl TEAM.
This fork is maintained by Ethan Mick.
If you need any help please contact us at info@creativelabs.pl (or Ethan at ethanmski@gmail.com)

This is a beta version of CLCascade library

Simple projects
===============

